The paper deals with a problem related to graph algorithms and combinatorial optimization, specifically on trees. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The problem also involves graph theory and combinatorics, which suggests categories such as cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) and cs.CC (Computational Complexity). The paper also mentions approximation algorithms, which could place it in cs.CG (Computational Geometry) or cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory).
